#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "BookMan: Organize your Bookmarks"
msgstr "BookMan: Organizirajte svoje zaznamke"

#. Tag: primary
#: bookmarks.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks"
msgstr "Zaznamki"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"BookMan is &krusader;'s Bookmark tool for bookmarking folders, local and "
"<link linkend=\"remote-connections\">remote &URL;s</link>, and later "
"returning to them in a click of a button. The Bookman menu is divided into "
"four sections:"
msgstr ""
"BookMan je &krusader;-jevo orodje za ustvarjanje zaznamkov za ustvarjanje "
"zaznamkov v mapah, lokalnih in <link linkend=\"remote-connections"
"\">oddaljenih &URL;-jih</link>, in kasnejše vrnitev nanje z enim klikom "
"gumba. Meni Bookman je razdeljen na štiri dele:"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid "Your personal bookmarks"
msgstr "Vaši osebni zaznamki"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Popular &URL;s</para>"
msgstr "<para>Priljubljeni &URL;</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Permanent bookmarks</para>"
msgstr "<para>Trajni zaznamki</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Manage bookmarks</para>"
msgstr "<para>Upravljanje zaznamkov</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can bookmark inside a remote file system (&FTP; or SAMBA) and later use "
"the bookmark to quickly connect to the remote machine, but you cannot "
"bookmark inside an archive."
msgstr ""
"Znotraj oddaljenega datotečnega sistema (&FTP; ali SAMBA) lahko dodate "
"zaznamek in pozneje uporabite zaznamek za hitro povezavo z oddaljenim "
"računalnikom, vendar ne morete dodati zaznamka znotraj arhiva."

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Bookmark menu</title>"
msgstr "<title>Meni zaznamkov</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: bookmarks.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Bookmark menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni zaznamkov</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Bookmarks"
msgstr "Uporaba zaznamkov"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Usually, you click on the <guibutton>BookMan II</guibutton> button (the "
"rightmost button to the right of the address bar at the top of the active "
"panel) when you are in the target folder. For example, to bookmark <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr/tmp</filename>, navigate &krusader; there and click "
"the <guibutton>BookMan II</guibutton> button and select "
"<guimenuitem>Bookmark Current</guimenuitem>. When the <guilabel>Add "
"Bookmark</guilabel> dialog box appears, the &URL; line will say <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr/tmp</filename>. <guilabel>Name</guilabel> is for "
"the name you would like to give to the bookmark (&eg;: temporary folder). "
"Hotkeys are supported by adding <literal>&amp;</literal> to the bookmark "
"name &eg; <literal>&amp;sourceforge, &amp;home, down&amp;loads</literal> "
"&etc;, so you can quickly call the bookmark name with <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>foo</keycap></keycombo>. If you add the bookmark "
"without entering a name, the bookmarks name will be the same as its target. "
"<guilabel>&URL;</guilabel> is where the bookmark points to. <guilabel>Create "
"in</guilabel> creates bookmark folders for organizing your bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"Običajno kliknete gumb <guibutton>BookMan II</guibutton> (skrajni desni gumb "
"desno od naslovne vrstice na vrhu aktivne plošče), ko ste v ciljni mapi. Če "
"želite na primer dodati <filename class=\"directory\">/usr/tmp</filename> "
"med zaznamke, poiščite &krusader; tam in kliknite gumb <guibutton>BookMan "
"II</guibutton> in izberite <guimenuitem>Zaznamek trenutno</guimenuitem>. Ko "
"se prikaže pogovorno okno <guilabel>Dodaj zaznamek</guilabel>, se &URL; "
"vrstica bo pisalo <filename class=\"directory\">/usr/tmp</filename>. "
"<guilabel>Ime</guilabel> je ime, ki ga želite dati zaznamku (&eg;: začasna "
"mapa). Bližnjice so podprte z dodajanjem <literal>&amp;</literal> imenu "
"zaznamka &eg; <literal>&amp;sourceforge, &amp;home, down&amp;loads</"
"literal>&etc;, tako da lahko hitro pokličete ime zaznamka s <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>foo</keycap></keycombo>. Če dodate zaznamek brez "
"vnosa imena, bo ime zaznamka enako njegovemu cilju. <guilabel>&URL;</"
"guilabel> je mesto, kamor kaže zaznamek. <guilabel>Ustvari v</guilabel> "
"ustvari mape z zaznamki za organiziranje vaših zaznamkov."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use your bookmarks, click the <guibutton>BookMan II</guibutton> button "
"and choose a bookmark. You may also use the <link linkend=\"key_bindings"
"\">Key-Bindings</link>: <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>B</"
"keycap></keycombo> to bookmark the current item, <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt; <keycap>right/left arrow</keycap></keycombo> to open right/left "
"panel bookmarks list and <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>D</"
"keycap></keycombo> to open the bookmarks of the active panel. From the "
"context menu of the bookmark (&RMB; click) you can open it in a new <link "
"linkend=\"folder-tabs\">Folder tab</link>."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo zaznamkov kliknite gumb <guibutton>BookMan II</guibutton> in "
"izberite zaznamek. Uporabite lahko tudi <link linkend=\"key_bindings\">veze "
"tipk</link>: <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> "
"za zaznamek trenutnega elementa, <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; "
"<keycap>puščica desno/levo</keycap></keycombo> za odpiranje seznama "
"zaznamkov na desni/levi plošči in <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>, da odprete zaznamke aktivne plošče. V "
"kontekstnem meniju zaznamka (&RMB; kliknite) ga lahko odprete v novem <link "
"linkend=\"folder-tabs\">zavihku Mapa</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is a quick search bar at the top of the <guibutton>BookMan II</"
"guibutton> menu."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu menija <guibutton>BookMan II</guibutton> je vrstica za hitro iskanje."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The search bar will always be visible in the bookmarks menu if you check the "
"corresponding item on the <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-general\">Panel "
"Konfigurator's page</link>."
msgstr ""
"Iskalna vrstica bo vedno vidna v meniju z zaznamki, če označite ustrezen "
"element na <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-general\">strani konfiguratorja "
"plošč</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Below are the rules to handle bookmarks:"
msgstr "Spodaj so navedena pravila za ravnanje z zaznamki:"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Just type letters to search: bookmarks are matched by name prefix"
msgstr "Za iskanje samo vnesite črke: zaznamki se ujemajo s predpono imena"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If multiple bookmarks are matched by the prefix, they are highlighted and "
"the first one is selected - hit &Enter; to activate the bookmark"
msgstr ""
"Če se s predpono ujema več zaznamkov, so označeni in izbran je prvi - "
"pritisnite &Enter; da aktivirate zaznamek"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once a single bookmark is matched, it is immediately triggered. That is when "
"you type <literal>'h'</literal> and only one bookmark starts with "
"<literal>'h'</literal>, it is executed immediately - no &Enter; needed"
msgstr ""
"Ko se en zaznamek ujema, se takoj sproži. Ko vnesete <literal>'h'</literal> "
"in se samo en zaznamek začne z <literal>'h'</literal>, se izvede takoj - "
"brez &Enter; potrebno"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accelerators work only if the keystroke is the first one"
msgstr "Pospeševalniki delujejo le, če je tipka pritisnjena prva"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Backspace; is supported"
msgstr "&Backspace; je podprt"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Search is case insensitive unless you type a capital letter. That is typing "
"<literal>HamBurglar</literal> will only match <literal>HamBurglar</literal> "
"but not <literal>hamburglar</literal> or <literal>Hamburglar</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Iskanje ne razlikuje med velikimi in malimi črkami, razen če vnesete veliko "
"začetnico. To pomeni, da se bo vnos <literal>HamBurglar</literal> ujemal "
"samo z <literal>HamBurglar</literal>, ne pa tudi z <literal>hamburglar</"
"literal> ali <literal>Hamburglar</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search bar is intentionally a read-only field"
msgstr "Iskalna vrstica je namenoma polje samo za branje"

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Password handling"
msgstr "Upravljanje z geslom"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One of the benefits of the <link linkend=\"bookman\">bookmark manager</link> "
"is that the passwords are saved using &plasma;'s services - where &eg; your "
"&konqueror;/&kmail; password are saved. If you have a wallet, &plasma; will "
"save the passwords there. By clicking the bookmarks, a dialog will open and "
"ask for your username and password. Supply them and click <guibutton>Save "
"password</guibutton>. The passwords and usernames will be saved securely by "
"&plasma;'s wallet (make sure it is enabled by your distro). The downside "
"here is that if the system was reinstalled and you do not backup your "
"passwords from the wallet as well as &krusader;'s bookmark file, something "
"will be lost."
msgstr ""
"Ena od prednosti <link linkend=\"bookman\">upravitelja zaznamkov</link> je "
"ta, da se gesla shranjujejo s storitvami &plasma; - kjer &eg; vaš "
"&konqueror;/&kmail; geslo je shranjeno. Če imate denarnico, &plasma; bo tam "
"shranil gesla. S klikom na zaznamke se odpre pogovorno okno, ki zahteva "
"uporabniško ime in geslo. Vnesite jih in kliknite <guibutton>Shrani geslo</"
"guibutton>. Gesla in uporabniška imena bodo varno shranjena v denarnici "
"&plasma; (prepričajte se, da jo vaš distro omogoča). Slaba stran je, da če "
"je bil sistem znova nameščen in ne varnostno kopirate svojih gesel iz "
"denarnice in datoteke z zaznamki &krusader;, se bo nekaj izgubilo."

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Popular &URL;s</title>"
msgstr "<title>Priljubljeni &URL;-ji</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: bookmarks.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Popular &URL;s</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Priljubljeni &URL;</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The submenu <guilabel>Popular &URL;s</guilabel> holds persistent the most "
"popular visited &URL;s (local or remote). This submenu displays the top 15 "
"popular &URL;s, sorted by ranking, so that the top &URL; is the most "
"popular. This is easy for when you need to visit &URL;s often, but do not "
"want to create <link linkend=\"bookman\">Bookmarks</link>, it serves as a "
"temporary bookmark list for the most visited links. Quicksearch in "
"<guilabel>Popular &URL;s</guilabel> is a fast way to browse/select the "
"popular &URL;s:"
msgstr ""
"Podmeni <guilabel>Priljubljeni &URL;-ji</guilabel> ohranja obstojne najbolj "
"priljubljene obiskane &URL;-je (lokalne ali oddaljene). V tem podmeniju je "
"prikazanih 15 najbolj priljubljenih &URL;, razvrščenih po uvrstitvi, tako da "
"je najboljši &URL; je najbolj priljubljena. To je enostavno, ko morate "
"pogosto obiskati URL-je, vendar ne želite ustvarjati <link linkend=\"bookman"
"\">zaznamkov</link>, saj služi kot začasen seznam zaznamkov za najbolj "
"obiskane povezave. Hitro iskanje v <guilabel>Priljubljenih &URL;-jih</"
"guilabel> je hiter način za brskanje/izbiranje priljubljenih &URL;-jev:"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the <guilabel>Popular &URL;s</guilabel> or use <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo>"
msgstr ""
"Odprite <guilabel>Priljubljene &URL;</guilabel> ali uporabite <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo>"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type a few letters to narrow the search"
msgstr "Vnesite nekaj črk, da zožite iskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press &Enter; (you will go to the &URL; from list)"
msgstr "Pritisnite &Enter; (odprli boste &URL; s seznama)"

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Permanent bookmarks</title>"
msgstr "<title>Trajni zaznamki</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are hardcoded bookmarks to the top bookmark menu; there is no need for "
"them to be saved to the file. With the <link linkend=\"context-menu"
"\">Context Menu</link> you can enable/disable these permanent bookmarks. The "
"following permanent bookmarks are available:"
msgstr ""
"To so trdo kodirani zaznamki v zgornjem meniju zaznamkov; ni jih treba "
"shraniti v datoteko. S <link linkend=\"context-menu\">kontekstnim menijem</"
"link> lahko omogočite/onemogočite te trajne zaznamke. Na voljo so naslednji "
"trajni zaznamki:"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Trash bin</guilabel> uses &plasma;'s <filename>trash:/</filename> "
"protocol."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Koš za smeti</guilabel> uporablja protokol &plasma; "
"<filename>trash:/</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Local Network</guilabel> uses &plasma;'s <filename>remote:/</"
"filename> protocol."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Lokalno omrežje</guilabel> uporablja &plasma; protokol "
"<filename>remote:/</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Virtual Filesystem</guilabel> <link linkend=\"vfs\">Virtual file "
"systems (VFS)</link> <filename>virt:/</filename> is not a virtual folder, "
"but a container for &URL;s from different file systems. It is used for &eg; "
"the <guilabel>Feed to Listbox</guilabel> feature of the search module and "
"the synchronizer. The location toolbar will display &eg; <filename>virt:/"
"Search results 1</filename> or <filename>virt:/Synchronise results 1</"
"filename>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Navidezni datotečni sistem</guilabel> <link linkend=\"vfs"
"\">Navidezni datotečni sistemi (VFS)</link> <filename>virt:/</filename> ni "
"navidezna mapa, temveč vsebnik za &URL; iz različnih datotečnih sistemov. "
"Uporablja se za &eg; funkcija <guilabel>Podaj v seznamsko polje</guilabel> "
"iskalnega modula in sinhronizatorja. Orodna vrstica lokacije bo prikazala "
"&eg; <filename>virt:/Rezultati iskanja 1</filename> ali <filename>virt:/"
"Sinhroniziraj rezultate 1</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Jump back</guilabel> or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> brings you back to your starting position when "
"you did create a new tab in the panel window. This feature is very handy if "
"you go deep into a folder tree, then you can return with one action to the "
"starting point. With <guilabel>Set jump back point here</guilabel> or "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> sets "
"the current folder as a jump back point."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Skoči nazaj</guilabel> ali <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> vas vrne na začetni položaj, ko ste ustvarili "
"nov zavihek v oknu plošče. Ta funkcija je zelo priročna, če greste globoko v "
"drevo map, potem se lahko z enim dejanjem vrnete na začetno točko. Z "
"<guilabel>Tukaj nastavite točko skoka nazaj</guilabel> ali <keycombo action="
"\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> nastavi trenutno mapo "
"kot točko za skok nazaj."

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Manage bookmarks</title>"
msgstr "<title>Upravljanje zaznamkov</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To edit and organize your bookmarks, by clicking the <guibutton>BookMan II</"
"guibutton> button and selecting the <guimenuitem>Manage Bookmarks</"
"guimenuitem>, <application>KeditBookmarks</application> will be displayed. "
"This is where you can edit/remove and rearrange the bookmarks. "
"<application>KeditBookmarks</application> is a bookmark editor for "
"&konqueror;, &krusader; and other applications, which use the <ulink url="
"\"http://grail.sourceforge.net/info/xbel.html\">XBEL standard</ulink> for "
"the bookmark format. The bookmarks are stored in <filename> ~/.local/share/"
"krusader/krbookmarks.xml</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti in organizirati svoje zaznamke, s klikom na gumb "
"<guibutton>BookMan II</guibutton> in izbiro <guimenuitem>Upravljanje "
"zaznamkov</guimenuitem> se prikaže <application>KeditBookmarks</"
"application>. Tukaj lahko urejate/odstranjujete in preurejate zaznamke. "
"<application>KeditBookmarks</application> je urejevalnik zaznamkov za "
"&konqueror;, &krusader; in druge aplikacije, ki uporabljajo <ulink url="
"\"http://grail.sourceforge.net/info/xbel.html\">standard XBEL</ulink> za "
"obliko zaznamkov. Zaznamki so shranjeni v <filename> ~/.local/share/krusader/"
"krbookmarks.xml</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default folder for the bookmarks file <filename>krusader/krbookmarks."
"xml</filename> is <filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/share</filename>. "
"You can determine the needed folder in your system using the "
"<userinput>qtpaths --paths GenericDataLocation</userinput> command in "
"terminal."
msgstr ""
"Privzeta mapa za datoteko z zaznamki <filename>krusader/krbookmarks.xml</"
"filename> je <filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/share</filename>. "
"Zahtevano mapo v vašem sistemu lahko določite z ukazom <userinput>qtpaths --"
"paths GenericDataLocation</userinput> v terminalu."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This local file exists only if you have edited &krusader; bookmarks. It will "
"be created after the first run of <application>KeditBookmarks</application> "
"from &krusader;."
msgstr ""
"Ta lokalna datoteka obstaja le, če ste uredili &krusader; zaznamki. "
"Ustvarjen bo po prvem zagonu <application>KeditBookmarks</application> iz "
"&krusader;."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default system bookmarks are stored in the <filename>kfileplaces/"
"bookmarks.xml</filename> file in the folder which can be determined using "
"the <userinput>qtpaths --paths GenericDataLocation</userinput> command."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti sistemski zaznamki so shranjeni v datoteki <filename>kfileplaces/"
"bookmarks.xml</filename> v mapi, ki jo lahko določite z ukazom "
"<userinput>qtpaths --paths GenericDataLocation</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<application>KeditBookmarks</application> is easy to use, however, if you "
"need more information, please read the <ulink url=\"help:/keditbookmarks/"
"index.html\">KeditBookmarks handbook</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<application>KeditBookmarks</application> je enostaven za uporabo, če pa "
"potrebujete več informacij, preberite <ulink url=\"help:/keditbookmarks/"
"index.html\">priročnik KeditBookmarks</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<title><application>KeditBookmarks</application> Bookmark Manager</title>"
msgstr ""
"<title><application>KeditBookmarks</application> Upravitelj zaznamkov</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: bookmarks.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase><application>KeditBookmarks</application> Bookmark Manager</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase><application>KeditBookmarks</application> Upravitelj zaznamkov</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks as action buttons on the Toolbar"
msgstr "Zaznamki kot akcijski gumbi v orodni vrstici"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bookmarks can be placed as buttons on the <link linkend=\"mainwindow\">Main "
"Toolbar</link> or the <link linkend=\"actions_toolbar\">Actions Toolbar</"
"link>. You can even make a key-binding for them:"
msgstr ""
"Zaznamke lahko postavite kot gumbe v <link linkend=\"mainwindow\">Glavno "
"orodno vrstico</link> ali <link linkend=\"actions_toolbar\">Orodno vrstico z "
"dejanji</link>. Zanje lahko naredite celo vezavo ključev:"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create your <link linkend=\"bookman\">Bookmarks</link>."
msgstr "Ustvarite svoje <link linkend=\"bookman\">zaznamke</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want, create keybindings for the bookmarks in the <link linkend="
"\"key_bindings\">Configure Shortcuts</link> window "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite, ustvarite povezave tipk za zaznamke v oknu <link linkend="
"\"key_bindings\">Konfiguriraj bližnjice</link> "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"bližnjice ...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add your bookmarks as action buttons on the <link linkend=\"mainwindow"
"\">Main Toolbar</link> or the <link linkend=\"actions_toolbar\">Actions "
"Toolbar</link> with the <guilabel>Configure Toolbars...</guilabel> window "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte svoje zaznamke kot gumbe dejanj v <link linkend=\"mainwindow"
"\">glavni orodni vrstici</link> ali <link linkend=\"actions_toolbar\">orodni "
"vrstici dejanj</link> z <guilabel>Konfiguriraj orodne vrstice ...</guilabel> "
"okno (<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"orodne vrstice ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
